==English==
===Proper noun===
'''Thames'''

# [[River]] in South [[England]] flowing 336 [[km]] (209 [[mile|mi.]]) through [[London]] to the [[North Sea]].
# [[River]] in [[Ontario]] province, [[Canada]], flowing 258 [[km]] (160 [[mile|mi.]]) to Lake [[St. Clair]].
# [[Estuary]] in the U.S. State of [[Connecticut]] flowing 24 [[km]] (15 [[mile|mi.]]) past [[New London]] to [[Long Island Sound]].

